<plot>A docudrama about Emma Bardac, the woman who had affairs with Georges Bizet and Gabriel Faure and was later married to Claude Debussy. The Labeque sisters play both themselves and the daughters of Emma Bardac. Musical numbers are performed while the camera explores French Impressionistic masterpieces and magnificent gardens.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?572929</url></doc>
